from a five-star hotel restaurant.

610
00:36:46,705 --> 00:36:47,789
Sounds great.

611
00:36:48,790 --> 00:36:49,916
Are you all excited?

612
00:36:49,999 --> 00:36:51,584
-Yes!
-Yes!

613
00:36:51,668 --> 00:36:53,628
Then I'll see you at the ceremony.

614
00:36:53,712 --> 00:36:55,380
-Yes!
-Yes!

615
00:36:58,091 --> 00:37:00,510
I booked a hotel room for the weekend.

616
00:37:00,593 --> 00:37:02,762
I won't pick up even if he calls.

617
00:37:04,013 --> 00:37:05,640
You, Won-jae, and Hyun-joo.

618
00:37:05,724 --> 00:37:07,726
Turn your phones off, all right?

619
00:37:07,809 --> 00:37:10,145
<i><font color="white">-Mission complete, ma'am.</font></i>
-Okay.

620
00:37:32,041 --> 00:37:34,127
Hello, A-hyun. This is Chun Jane.

621
00:37:36,129 --> 00:37:38,631
It's a shame we couldn't talk
when you visited.

622
00:37:38,715 --> 00:37:40,467
If you have time…

623
00:37:43,178 --> 00:37:45,680
You're leaving in two days?

624
00:37:47,223 --> 00:37:48,933
Then before you do…

625
00:37:50,310 --> 00:37:51,603
Wait, where?

626
00:37:59,694 --> 00:38:00,820
You'll do what?

627
00:38:00,904 --> 00:38:03,531
I'd like to sing
at the president's inauguration ceremony.

628
00:38:03,615 --> 00:38:05,074
Exactly. Why?

629
00:38:05,158 --> 00:38:07,410
I hear Director Oh Hun will be there.

630
00:38:07,494 --> 00:38:10,163
After he listens to me sing,

631
00:38:10,246 --> 00:38:14,375
you can talk him up to see what he thinks.

632
00:38:14,459 --> 00:38:16,795
Well… One second.

633
00:38:18,755 --> 00:38:19,923
Hello, Producer Nah.

634
00:38:22,675 --> 00:38:23,635
What?

635
00:38:34,270 --> 00:38:35,939
Yes, Producer Nah. Okay.

636
00:38:36,022 --> 00:38:37,190
All right.

637
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:41,611
Joo-ryoung, have this.

638
00:38:42,237 --> 00:38:43,446
It's your usual.

639
00:38:46,241 --> 00:38:48,535
Thanks a lot, Jung-don.

640
00:38:49,244 --> 00:38:50,662
-Let's go.
-Okay.

641
00:38:53,581 --> 00:38:55,834
Producer Nah is
going out of the city next week,

642
00:38:56,543 --> 00:38:59,045
