before he leaves.

643
00:39:02,423 --> 00:39:03,424
Okay.

644
00:39:03,508 --> 00:39:04,592
Joo-ryoung.

645
00:39:05,093 --> 00:39:07,929
Nobody knows about your fear of heights
except for me.

646
00:39:08,972 --> 00:39:12,600
Keep up your counseling, and you'll be
better by the time you leave the country.

647
00:39:12,684 --> 00:39:13,726
So don't worry.

648
00:39:14,477 --> 00:39:15,770
All right.

649
00:39:18,815 --> 00:39:21,568
Anyway, where's Won-jae?
Why are you driving?

