655
00:39:38,877 --> 00:39:42,547
but I just remembered
because you mentioned it!

656
00:39:44,007 --> 00:39:45,049
Hey.

657
00:39:52,557 --> 00:39:55,101
INAUGURATION CEREMONY

658
00:40:01,316 --> 00:40:02,442
Hello.

659
00:40:04,944 --> 00:40:06,529
