663
00:40:16,789 --> 00:40:18,291
Producer Nah, you're here.

664
00:40:18,374 --> 00:40:20,209
-Hello.
-Hello.

665
00:40:20,293 --> 00:40:22,545
-Director Ma, you're also here.
-Hello, Joo-ryoung.

666
00:40:22,629 --> 00:40:25,048
-So you came.
