667
00:40:25,131 --> 00:40:27,508
I love the ambiance of this ceremony.

668
00:40:27,592 --> 00:40:29,552
I should go to Method
for <i><font color="white">Business Trip to Work</font></i>.

669
00:40:29,636 --> 00:40:31,512
Sure, come by anytime.

670
00:40:32,263 --> 00:40:34,390
And President Bae of SY Pictures.

671
00:40:34,474 --> 00:40:35,850
I've heard a lot about you.

672
00:40:35,934 --> 00:40:38,686
-Hello.
-Yes, it's an honor to meet you.

