I had to come because of Joo-ryoung.

679
00:40:58,081 --> 00:41:00,083
I came to talk to President Bae too.

680
00:41:00,166 --> 00:41:01,584
To talk? About what?

681
00:41:03,628 --> 00:41:07,006
President Bae and I will work together.
A co-production.

682
00:41:08,049 --> 00:41:10,343
I'll tell President Koo later,
so keep it quiet.

683
00:41:10,426 --> 00:41:13,388
And let's pretend
we didn't see each other today.

684
00:41:13,471 --> 00:41:14,555
Okay?

685
00:41:21,145 --> 00:41:22,230
You traitors.

686
00:41:22,313 --> 00:41:24,023
And you were the one
who talked everyone into this.

687
00:41:24,107 --> 00:41:25,233
