697
00:41:43,167 --> 00:41:44,836
Microphone test.

698
00:41:44,919 --> 00:41:46,295
All right.

699
00:41:46,379 --> 00:41:48,798
And now, let us begin
the inauguration ceremony

700
00:41:48,881 --> 00:41:52,010
for President Koo Hae-jun
of Method Entertainment.

701
00:41:52,093 --> 00:41:55,763
