705
00:42:17,577 --> 00:42:20,913
First off, I'd like to thank everyone who…

706
00:42:28,629 --> 00:42:30,631
Yes, nice to meet you.

707
00:42:30,715 --> 00:42:32,341
Why am I suddenly sweating?

708
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:36,137
Producer Nah, thank you.

709
00:42:37,513 --> 00:42:41,059
