along with his ceremony.

724
00:43:30,483 --> 00:43:32,276
So I said yes.

725
00:43:32,360 --> 00:43:34,904
<i><font color="white">I sent you the divorce papers.
Sign and return them.</font></i>

726
00:43:34,987 --> 00:43:38,199
