without me.

905
00:57:01,793 --> 00:57:02,836
I won't.

906
00:57:17,893 --> 00:57:19,102
My goodness.

907
00:57:19,186 --> 00:57:20,979
Somebody save me!

908
00:57:21,521 --> 00:57:23,523
Joo-ryoung!

909
00:57:24,191 --> 00:57:25,233
Oh, my.

910
00:57:25,317 --> 00:57:27,736
Jung-don, where have you been?

911
00:57:27,819 --> 00:57:29,404
How did you get up there?

912
00:57:29,488 --> 00:57:30,530
No idea.

913
00:57:31,198 --> 00:57:33,408
I was up here once I sobered up.

914
00:57:33,492 --> 00:57:36,203
Why did you go up there
when you're afraid of heights?

915
00:57:36,286 --> 00:57:38,080
Fear of heights? What?

916
00:57:38,789 --> 00:57:39,790
Goodness, Joo-ryoung.

917
00:57:39,873 --> 00:57:41,166
How did you get up there?

918
00:57:41,249 --> 00:57:43,502
-What's this about fear of heights?
-It's not that.

919
00:57:44,294 --> 00:57:45,754
No, stop it!

920
00:57:47,422 --> 00:57:48,340
Joo-ryoung.

921
00:57:49,883 --> 00:57:51,093
Just drop down.

922
00:57:51,760 --> 00:57:53,637
-What?
-Let go of your hands.

923
00:57:54,763 --> 00:57:56,431
Remember what the doctor said?

924
00:57:57,766 --> 00:58:00,352
Joo-ryoung, don't try so hard.

925
00:58:01,228 --> 00:58:02,521
You've done well enough.

926
00:58:03,105 --> 00:58:04,564
You know that.

927
00:58:04,648 --> 00:58:07,275
Let go. Just let it all go, Joo-ryoung!

928
00:58:09,778 --> 00:58:11,113
Joo-ryoung.

929
00:58:11,196 --> 00:58:12,906
I'm right here. I have you.

930
00:58:13,865 --> 00:58:15,659
Joo-ryoung, let's do it together.

931
00:58:16,410 --> 00:58:17,786
I'll hold you tight.

932
00:58:17,869 --> 00:58:19,621
I'll catch you.

933
00:58:20,831 --> 00:58:22,040
Let go.

934
00:58:22,124 --> 00:58:25,293
Okay. I'll try.

935
00:58:26,086 --> 00:58:27,379
You can do this, Joo-ryoung.

936
00:59:09,755 --> 00:59:11,423
Are you all right?

937
00:59:16,303 --> 00:59:17,137
Yes.

938
00:59:23,018 --> 00:59:24,644
So where's Jung-don?

939
00:59:30,817 --> 00:59:31,818
Joo-ryoung.

940
00:59:33,070 --> 00:59:35,363
-Are you okay?
-Hey.

941
00:59:36,865 --> 00:59:39,034
Were you here like this?

942
00:59:41,161 --> 00:59:42,496
Jung-don.

943
00:59:43,997 --> 00:59:46,666
Thank you, Jung-don.

944
00:59:46,750 --> 00:59:48,001
Great job.

945
00:59:48,085 --> 00:59:50,545
-Thank you.
-No problem.

946
00:59:54,966 --> 00:59:57,219
I'm finally sobering up.

947
01:00:00,013 --> 01:00:01,598
It's really effective.

948
01:00:01,681 --> 01:00:04,017
It is. Thanks.

949
01:00:15,237 --> 01:00:16,279
Jung-don.

950
01:00:18,156 --> 01:00:19,741
You know that

951
01:00:20,700 --> 01:00:22,911
when I was about to give up

952
01:00:22,994 --> 01:00:26,873
on 20 years of my career as an actor,

953
01:00:27,582 --> 01:00:29,501
I took on <i><font color="white">Squid Game</font></i>.

954
01:00:30,752 --> 01:00:33,880
I thought, "Fine, I'll do this and quit."

955
01:00:33,964 --> 01:00:38,969
That's why I did my best
and gave it my all.

956
01:00:41,304 --> 01:00:42,806
Of course I know, Joo-ryoung.

957
01:00:43,348 --> 01:00:45,517
It was tough for me just watching you.

958
01:00:48,603 --> 01:00:51,273
After <i><font color="white">Squid Game</font></i> became a huge hit,

959
01:00:51,356 --> 01:00:54,442
I was very grateful and happy

960
01:00:55,735 --> 01:00:58,613
that people loved and welcomed me,

961
01:00:59,614 --> 01:01:00,949
but I was also afraid.

962
01:01:02,576 --> 01:01:04,661
Afraid it would go back to the way it was.

963
01:01:06,079 --> 01:01:08,707
That's nonsense. Why would you think that?

964
01:01:09,499 --> 01:01:12,294
Joo-ryoung, this is just the beginning.

965
01:01:13,086 --> 01:01:15,589
You're an actor that makes people
anticipate your next role.

966
01:01:15,672 --> 01:01:17,174
I know it for sure.

967
01:01:18,884 --> 01:01:22,554
So you have to believe in yourself
and march forward.

968
01:01:24,806 --> 01:01:26,683
Do you think I can really do a good job?

969
01:01:27,434 --> 01:01:30,061
I know because
I've been with you to this day.

970
01:01:30,145 --> 01:01:31,062
Also,

971
01:01:31,771 --> 01:01:33,648
don't try so hard.

972
01:01:38,653 --> 01:01:39,779
Jung-don.

973
01:01:41,072 --> 01:01:41,948
I am…

974
01:01:43,450 --> 01:01:45,994
so glad that you're my agent.

975
01:01:47,495 --> 01:01:48,538
Me too.

976
01:01:49,289 --> 01:01:50,332
Thanks.

977
01:01:51,666 --> 01:01:52,959
Thank you, I mean it.

978
01:01:53,043 --> 01:01:54,961
Why are you like this today?

979
01:01:55,045 --> 01:01:56,963
-Let's go.
-Shall we?

980
01:02:04,471 --> 01:02:05,513
Right.

981
01:02:06,306 --> 01:02:10,393
Producer Nah just heard
that I have a fear of heights. What now?

982
01:02:10,477 --> 01:02:13,063
I'll talk to him once again.

983
01:02:13,146 --> 01:02:14,814
I think it'll be more interesting.

984
01:02:18,735 --> 01:02:22,322
What's so fun about watching someone
do what they're good at.

985
01:02:22,822 --> 01:02:25,116
It's more touching to see
someone muster up courage

986
01:02:25,200 --> 01:02:28,787
and overcome their fears. Isn't that so?

987
01:02:29,496 --> 01:02:30,956
Gosh, Producer Nah.

988
01:02:32,666 --> 01:02:35,585
Let's fly through the sky in style.

989
01:02:36,920 --> 01:02:38,129
Sorry?

990
01:02:38,213 --> 01:02:39,506
The sky?

991
01:02:39,589 --> 01:02:40,882
-Why would I fly?
-What?

992
01:02:40,966 --> 01:02:42,801
-Producer Nah.
-Producer Nah.

993
01:02:42,884 --> 01:02:44,094
Did you say the sky?

994
01:02:45,178 --> 01:02:47,264
Yung-suk!

995
01:02:47,347 --> 01:02:49,099
-Producer Nah!
-Wait, Yung-suk!

996
01:02:49,182 --> 01:02:50,892
No, I can't fly!

997
01:03:16,793 --> 01:03:19,087
Director Ma, why don't you lead

998
01:03:19,754 --> 01:03:21,965
the co-production with SY Pictures?

999
01:03:25,760 --> 01:03:27,053
I think you'll do great.

1000
01:03:30,807 --> 01:03:33,226
<i><font color="white">I take off my school uniform…</font></i>

1001
01:03:44,821 --> 01:03:46,197
Traitor. Renegade.

1002
01:03:46,865 --> 01:03:48,908
The managers and Director Ma
were there too.

1003
01:03:48,992 --> 01:03:51,828
-Why are you so harsh with us?
-Exactly.

1004
01:03:51,911 --> 01:03:53,580
-Eun-soo.
-Traitor.

1005
01:03:53,663 --> 01:03:55,498
I'm sorry.

1006
01:03:57,500 --> 01:04:00,128
Gosh, how much did she drink?

1007
01:04:04,507 --> 01:04:06,259
-Did you get home well?
-I did.

1008
01:04:06,343 --> 01:04:08,053
-Did you have fun?
-Yes.

1009
01:04:09,846 --> 01:04:11,181
I had fun too.

1010
01:04:19,731 --> 01:04:20,815
Hey, Suk.

1011
01:04:21,483 --> 01:04:22,776
Drink this and sober up.

1012
01:04:22,859 --> 01:04:24,235
I'm dying here.

1013
01:04:24,944 --> 01:04:27,072
You drank like a fish.

1014
01:04:29,157 --> 01:04:31,785
Hey, you got sauce on your hair.

1015
01:04:34,996 --> 01:04:36,456
How did you come here?

1016
01:04:36,539 --> 01:04:38,750
What are you spewing?
I got us hangover drinks.

1017
01:04:39,918 --> 01:04:42,462
Why are you so late?

1018
01:04:42,545 --> 01:04:44,881
I missed you so much.

1019
01:04:44,964 --> 01:04:48,218
You're wasted. A goner. Goodness.

1020
01:04:48,927 --> 01:04:51,054
I'm sorry for everything.

1021
01:04:53,014 --> 01:04:55,433
So don't ever leave without me.

1022
01:04:56,101 --> 01:04:57,685
What the hell are you saying? Hey!

1023
01:04:58,812 --> 01:05:00,313
Hey, what's with you?

1024
01:05:32,011 --> 01:05:36,057
<i><font color="white">Actor Park Chun-bae,
who starred in </font></i> Rainbow Bridge,

1025
01:05:36,141 --> 01:05:40,812
<i><font color="white">was nominated for Best Supporting Actor
at the Golden Film Festival.</font></i>

1026
01:05:41,729 --> 01:05:46,484
<i><font color="white">He was a lesser-known actor who endured
a 30-year career outside of the spotlight.</font></i>

1027
01:05:46,568 --> 01:05:47,652
<i><font color="white">That's all for today.</font></i>

1028
01:05:54,117 --> 01:05:56,786
BEHIND EVERY STAR

1029
01:06:20,894 --> 01:06:22,228
-That day…
-It was a mistake.

1030
01:06:22,312 --> 01:06:23,521
And I already love someone else.

1031
01:06:23,605 --> 01:06:25,857
The tax guy? What about kissing?
Was I first? Who did you kiss first?

1032
01:06:25,940 --> 01:06:29,110
<i><font color="white">-Director Oh Hun? Just the two of you?
-This is a restricted area.</font></i>

1033
01:06:29,194 --> 01:06:30,361
<i><font color="white">Do you feel like he's taken her?</font></i>

1034
01:06:30,445 --> 01:06:34,157
Make sure Daniel Henney stars in this film
or I'll terminate his contract.

1035
01:06:34,240 --> 01:06:36,326
-Sorry, but I don't have time.
-Chun Je-suk!

1036
01:06:36,409 --> 01:06:39,871
<i><font color="white">Daniel must do this film.
We can't miss this. I'm dead serious.</font></i>

1037
01:06:39,954 --> 01:06:41,998
It's such an incredibly ridiculous idea.

1038
01:06:42,081 --> 01:06:43,541
Director Ye refuses to work with Daniel.

1039
01:06:43,625 --> 01:06:46,711
<i><font color="white">-What should we do?
-I think I can help.</font></i>

1040
01:06:48,630 --> 01:06:50,089
<i><font color="white">The real problem is So Hyun-joo.</font></i>

1041
01:06:50,173 --> 01:06:52,258
We can take legal action and fire her.

1042
